<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">śrīmānapparasākhyasya nandanaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></hi><note n="304-1">This hemistich is incomplete.</note> <hi rend="grantha">Āpastambasasva</hi><note n="304-2">Read <hi rend="grantha">‘ssva’</hi></note> <hi rend="grantha">sūtrēṇa bharadvājakulōtbhavaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> viṭṭappākhyō ma</hi>
<lb n="2" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">hāmantrī dvi<supplied reason="omitted">ja</supplied>mukhyō dayāparaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> kūlē dakṣiṇakāvēryyā Uttarē raṅgabhūtalē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīyōganārasimhasya</hi>
<lb n="3"/><hi rend="grantha">mandirāpaścimām bhuvam <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> krītvā śrīraṅganāthasya vi<unclear>śva</unclear>dhēnum vanam</hi><note n="304-3">A word of two letters is wanting to complete the hemistich</note><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

